  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t平江县还发一个募捐公告，称一方有难，八方支援。表示在这样的危急关头下，平江县众志成城，正在抗洪抢险，希望爱心人士伸出援助之手，踊跃捐款捐物，并且所有捐赠的款物由平江县红十字会和平江县民政局统一接收，全部用于平江县受灾群众恢复家园。该事件引发质疑，如果是你，你会选择捐款吗？<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvM2Y2ZGU0NTcxNzMyZWU2MmMxZmFlLnBuZz93aWR0aD02OTQmaGVpZ2h0PTczMQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3f6de4571732ee62c1fae.png?width=694&amp;height=731\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3f6de4571732ee62c1fae.png?width=694&amp;height=731\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3f6de4571732ee62c1fae.png?width=694&amp;height=731\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZmFkM2FiN2Q0MzczYWQwMTI2ODEyLmpwZz93aWR0aD0yMDkxJmhlaWdodD0xMjEy\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fad3ab7d4373ad0126812.jpg?width=2091&amp;height=1212\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fad3ab7d4373ad0126812.jpg?width=2091&amp;height=1212\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fad3ab7d4373ad0126812.jpg?width=2091&amp;height=1212\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzY3ODc0NGFhNzBjYjAxNmUxMDVhLnBuZz93aWR0aD04MTkmaGVpZ2h0PTM5MQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7678744aa70cb016e105a.png?width=819&amp;height=391\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7678744aa70cb016e105a.png?width=819&amp;height=391\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7678744aa70cb016e105a.png?width=819&amp;height=391\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
